
------------------------------ Cron job scheduler -----------------------------------------


1. Main cron process will be run as Daemon which will keep on scanning the crontab in the background.
2. Once there is a match between current time and specified time the corresponding command will be executed using system command.
3. Using mycrontab utility user can add , list , remove the crontab job entries.
4. All the output both command and any error will be send by system function to mycron.log file in home directory.